OL,3,CIslington flood: Council leader tells
OL,4,CThames Water to 'get your act together'
OL,6,FThe leader of Islington Council has
OL,7,Ftold Thames Water to "get your act
OL,8,Ftogether" after a burst water pipe
OL,9,Fleft residents and businesses on
OL,10,FCaledonian Road submerged in major
OL,11,Fflooding.
OL,13,FCllr Una O'Halloran wrote to Thames
OL,14,FWater boss Chris Weston "on behalf of
OL,15,Fthe hundreds of thousands of
OL,16,Fresidents" in the borough, accusing
OL,17,Fthe water company of years of "neglect
OL,18,Fand inaction".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
