CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772452963
OL,3,CIslington flood: Council leader tells
OL,4,CThames Water to 'get your act together'
OL,6,FIn the letter she said: "Caledonian
OL,7,FRoad is at the heart of our borough,
OL,8,Fand is a hustling, bustling street
OL,9,Ffilled with gloriously diverse
OL,10,Fresidents and businesses.
OL,12,F"But on Tuesday (24 Feburary), life on
OL,13,FCaledonian Road was turned upside
OL,14,Fdown, as water from a burst main
OL,15,Ffilled the streets.
OL,17,F"The scenes on the street resembled a
OL,18,Fdisaster movie, with emergency
OL,19,Fservices in boats rushing to rescue
OL,20,Fresidents from their properties.
OL,26,@tD@QpmtD@]pn
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772452963
OL,3,CIslington flood: Council leader tells
OL,4,CThames Water to 'get your act together'
OL,6,F"And this could have been prevented,
OL,7,Fhad it not been for years of Thames
OL,8,FWater neglect and inaction."
OL,10,FThousands of people were left without
OL,11,Fa stable source of water for more than
OL,12,F24 hours as Thames Water worked to fix
OL,13,Fthe major water main.
OL,15,FProperties within a hundred metre
OL,16,Fradius were evacuated, with some
OL,17,Fresidents being rescued by boat.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
