OL,3,CIslington flood: Council leader tells
OL,4,CThames Water to 'get your act together'
OL,6,FWhen they returned to assess the
OL,7,Fdamage - many found their homes
OL,8,Funinhabitable and their businesses in
OL,9,Fruin.
OL,11,FCllr O'Halloran called on Thames Water
OL,12,Fto address three main concerns:
OL,14,FShe also pointed to previous flooding
OL,15,Fin the borough, including in Angel,
OL,16,FHornsey Road, and Canonbury Street.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
