PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772452963
OL,3,CIslington flood: Council leader tells
OL,4,CThames Water to 'get your act together'
OL,6,FSigning off she said: "It's bad enough
OL,7,Fthat Thames Water profits `
OL,8,Fsignificantly ` from people's need for
OL,9,Fwater, but the disgraceful service
OL,10,Fthat you provide is unacceptable.
OL,12,F"We've had enough havoc and
OL,13,Fdisruption: Get your act together, and
OL,14,Fstart putting people before profits."
OL,16,FThames Water has been approached for
OL,17,Fcomment.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/5
